### Presidio API Test Requests
### Use with the VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@analyzerUrl  = http://localhost:5002
@anonymizerUrl = http://localhost:5001

### ─── Analyzer ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check - Analyzer
GET {{analyzerUrl}}/health

###

### Analyze text for PII entities
POST {{analyzerUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hi, I'm John Smith. My email is john.smith@example.com and my phone is 212-555-0199. My SSN is 078-05-1120.",
  "language": "en"
}

###

### Analyze with specific entity types only
POST {{analyzerUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Send the invoice to jane.doe@company.org or call 415-867-5309.",
  "language": "en",
  "entities": ["EMAIL_ADDRESS", "PHONE_NUMBER"]
}

###

### Analyze with score threshold
POST {{analyzerUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "My credit card number is 4111 1111 1111 1111, expiry 12/26.",
  "language": "en",
  "score_threshold": 0.5
}

###

### List all supported recognizers
GET {{analyzerUrl}}/recognizers?language=en

###

### List all supported entity types
GET {{analyzerUrl}}/supportedentities?language=en


### ─── Anonymizer ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check - Anonymizer
GET {{anonymizerUrl}}/health

###

### Anonymize (redact) PII - replace with entity type label
POST {{anonymizerUrl}}/anonymize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hi, I'm John Smith. My email is john.smith@example.com and my phone is 212-555-0199.",
  "anonymizers": {
    "DEFAULT": { "type": "replace" }
  },
  "analyzer_results": [
    { "start": 8,  "end": 18, "score": 0.85, "entity_type": "PERSON" },
    { "start": 32, "end": 54, "score": 1.0,  "entity_type": "EMAIL_ADDRESS" },
    { "start": 70, "end": 82, "score": 0.75, "entity_type": "PHONE_NUMBER" }
  ]
}

###

### Anonymize with MASK operator
POST {{anonymizerUrl}}/anonymize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "John's SSN is 078-05-1120.",
  "anonymizers": {
    "DEFAULT": {
      "type": "mask",
      "masking_char": "*",
      "chars_to_mask": 4,
      "from_end": true
    }
  },
  "analyzer_results": [
    { "start": 0,  "end": 4,  "score": 0.85, "entity_type": "PERSON" },
    { "start": 14, "end": 25, "score": 0.85, "entity_type": "US_SSN" }
  ]
}

###

### Anonymize with HASH operator
POST {{anonymizerUrl}}/anonymize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Contact jane.doe@company.org for details.",
  "anonymizers": {
    "EMAIL_ADDRESS": { "type": "hash", "hash_type": "sha256" }
  },
  "analyzer_results": [
    { "start": 8, "end": 27, "score": 1.0, "entity_type": "EMAIL_ADDRESS" }
  ]
}

###

### List supported anonymizers
GET {{anonymizerUrl}}/anonymizers
